Adding two tests that will use curl to make requests

The tests will occure after the deploy step

stage('Integration Tests - DEV') {
      steps {
        script {
          try {
            withKubeConfig([credentialsId: 'kubeconfig']) {
              sh "bash integration-test.sh"
            }
          } catch (e) {
            withKubeConfig([credentialsId: 'kubeconfig']) {
              sh "kubectl -n default rollout undo deploy ${deploymentName}"
            }
            throw e
          }
        }
      }
    }

If the tests fail then roll the deploy back
